Uses of Package
bluej.codecoverage.pref

  • Packages that use bluej.codecoverage.pref 
    Package Description
    bluej.codecoverage.main
    Contains classes for setting up the extension when BlueJ initializes it.
    bluej.codecoverage.pref
    Classes for accessing preferences defined in the option package.
    bluej.codecoverage.pref.option
    Contains classes that provide access to specific preferences.
    bluej.codecoverage.ui.main
    Classes for displaying the main report frame that appears after a Coverage session.
    bluej.codecoverage.ui.pref
    Class for the preference panel displayed by BlueJ.
